title: New Holland T4.110F Utility Tractor
item_description:
New Holland T4.110F Utility Tractor

  • Manufacturer: New Holland
  • Model: T4.110F
  • Hours: 2623
  • Drive type: 4WD
  • Front Bucket Size: 82”
  • Number of Tires: 4
  • Tire Size: Front: 10.5/80-18 Rear: 19.5L-24
  • Function Tested: Yes, see video

The following information about this model was obtained from tractordata.com and was not verified by West Auctions:

  • Engine: FPT 3.4L 4-cyl diesel
  • Engine power: 107 hp
  • Fuel Tank: 30.3 gal
  • PTO: 96 hp
  • Power Steering 
  • Wet disc brakes

Link to tractor data page: https://www.tractordata.com/farm-tractors/008/9/0/8908-new-holland-t4110.html

CARB Off-Road Diesel Disclosure Statement: “When operated in California, any off-road diesel vehicle may be subject to the California Air Resources Board In-Use Off-road Diesel Vehicle Regulation. It therefore could be subject to retrofit or accelerated turnover requirements to reduce emissions of air pollutants. For more information, please visit the California Air Resources Board website at http://www.arb.ca.gov/msprog/ordiesel/ordiesel.htm.”
